# Buildfiles help

Name:

   Pandaboard Mini Distribution

About:

   A minimal filesystem for the Pandaboard.

Main features:

   * Busybox utilities
   * Upstart init system
   * Dropbear SSH client/server

Main builds:

   fs      - Filesystem
   linux   - Linux kernel
   u-boot  - Bootloader

Quick build guide:

   buildgear build fs
   buildgear build linux
   buildgear build u-boot

Build options:

   None

Known issues:

   None

Filesystem layout:

   /usr/bin/            User command/application binaries
   /usr/sbin/           System binaries (e.g. daemons)
   /usr/lib/            Libraries
   /usr/include/        Header files
   /usr/lib/<prog>/     Plug-ins, addons, etc
   /usr/share/man/      Man pages
   /usr/share/<prog>/   Data files
   /usr/etc/<prog>/     Configuration files
   /etc/                Configuration files for system software (daemons, etc.)

Maintainer:

   Martin Lund <martin@martinlund.org>
